<section class="projects-section">
    <div class="projects-container">
        <div class="projects-grid">

            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">
        <!-- <img src="/public/images/amr.jpg" alt="Autonomous Mobile Robot"> -->
    </div>
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h2>Autonomous Mobile Robot (AMR)</h2>
                    <span class="status ongoing">Ongoing</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> An advanced autonomous mobile robot engineered specifically to streamline warehouse operations and material handling.</p>
                <p><strong>Tech Stack:</strong> ROS2, MATLAB, Simulink.</p>
                <div class="project-achievements">
                    <strong>Outcomes:</strong> Top 30 nationally at ROBOFEST Gujarat 2025 (secured ₹2.5 Lakhs in cash prizes). Provisional patent filed through BITS Pilani and GUJCOST.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">
        <!-- <img src="/images/projects/amr.jpg" alt="Autonomous Mobile Robot"> -->
    </div>
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h2>Lam Research Challenge 2025</h2>
                    <span class="status achievement">Top 12 Nationally</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> A highly structured R&D initiative tackling real-world industrial challenges in advanced research and development.</p>
                <p><strong>Specs:</strong> Demands elite-level problem-solving, bridging classroom theory with incredibly complex, open-ended industrial constraints.</p>
                <div class="project-achievements">
                    <strong>Outcomes:</strong> Finished in the Top 12 nationally out of more than 1,000 participating teams across India.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">
        <!-- <img src="/images/projects/amr.jpg" alt="Autonomous Mobile Robot"> -->
    </div>
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h2>Battle Bot (Maqsad)</h2>
                    <span class="status ongoing">Ongoing</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> A high-performance drum spinner BattleBot designed for close-combat scenarios.</p>
                <p><strong>Specs:</strong> Built with a robust chassis, high-torque motors, and a high-speed rotating drum weapon to withstand high loads.</p>
                <div class="project-achievements">
                    <strong>Deployment:</strong> Competed at IIT Roorkee's Techfest 'Cognizance'. Future iterations will explore autonomous targeting.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">
        <!-- <img src="/images/projects/amr.jpg" alt="Autonomous Mobile Robot"> -->
    </div>
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h2>High-Performance Drone</h2>
                    <span class="status completed">Deployed</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> A custom-built drone engineered for precision flight, rapid acceleration, and aerial maneuverability.</p>
                <p><strong>Specs:</strong> Advanced avionics, custom flight controllers, rigorous PCB assembly, and precision soldering.</p>
                <div class="project-achievements">
                    <strong>Deployment:</strong> Developed for high-stakes technical competitions like IIT Jodhpur's Prometeo.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">
        <!-- <img src="/images/projects/amr.jpg" alt="Autonomous Mobile Robot"> -->
    </div>
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h2>Line Follower V2</h2>
                    <span class="status completed">Completed / Recurring</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> A high-speed, precision-driven autonomous robot engineered to track and navigate complex path layouts.</p>
                <p><strong>Specs:</strong> Essential 2-3 month project for training incoming batches in core sensor integration and fast-response motor control.</p>
                <div class="project-achievements">
                    <strong>Outcomes:</strong> Represented BITS Pilani at Technoxian 9.0, competing against a massive pool of over 1,500 teams.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">
        <!-- <img src="/images/projects/amr.jpg" alt="Autonomous Mobile Robot"> -->
    </div>
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h2>Precision Pick & Place Bot</h2>
                    <span class="status completed">Deployed</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> A highly responsive bot designed to grasp, lift, and maneuver payloads into specific target zones under strict time constraints.</p>
                <p><strong>Specs:</strong> Tackles complex manipulator kinematics, actuator control, and cross-functional mechanical/electronics collaboration.</p>
                <div class="project-achievements">
                    <strong>Deployment:</strong> A staple competitor in national robotics arenas and events like Robolympics.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="project-card">
                <div class="project-image">
        <!-- <img src="/images/projects/amr.jpg" alt="Autonomous Mobile Robot"> -->
    </div>
                <div class="project-header">
                    <h2>Robosoccer Bot</h2>
                    <span class="status completed">Deployed</span>
                </div>
                <p><strong>Overview:</strong> A rugged, highly agile mobile robot engineered specifically for the high-speed, impact-heavy environment of robotic soccer.</p>
                <p><strong>Specs:</strong> Prioritizes drivetrain efficiency, low center of gravity, and durability against field collisions.</p>
                <div class="project-achievements">
                    <strong>Deployment:</strong> Competes at premier national tech fests, testing rapid design iteration.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
